OL,3,CReport finds underinvestment in
OL,4,CGuernsey fire service puts public at
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FUnderinvestment in Guernsey's Fire and
OL,8,FRescue Service (GFRS) has resulted in
OL,9,Fa risk to 'life and limb' if there is
OL,10,Fa serious incident, says an
OL,11,Findependent report.
OL,13,FThe report by the Local Government
OL,14,FAssociation (LGA) says there are
OL,15,Fcurrently 'foreseeable risks' that
OL,16,Fcould lead to incidents the GFRS won't
OL,17,Fbe able to 'safely and effectively'
OL,18,Fresolve without additional investment.
