OL,4,CGuernsey fire service puts public at
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FThe LGA was asked to do a peer review
OL,8,Fof the service to highlight any
OL,9,Fproblems and help it improve.
OL,11,FIt found its budget has only increased
OL,12,Fby #88,000 over the course of a
OL,13,Fdecade, significantly below the rate
OL,14,FRPI and equating to a significant
OL,15,Freduction in funding in real terms.
