OL,3,CReport finds underinvestment in
OL,4,CGuernsey fire service puts public at
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FThe reports states: "The Bailiwick
OL,8,Fcontains a wide variety of risks and
OL,9,Fcurrently the service cannot respond
OL,10,Feffectively to all of these. Put
OL,11,Fbluntly there is a risk to life and
OL,12,Flimb if there is a serious incident.
OL,13,FIt is an additional risk that a
OL,14,Fserious incident would adversely
OL,15,Fdamage the reputation of States of
OL,16,FGuernsey to a worldwide audience."
