OL,7,FIt comes just four months after
OL,8,FJersey's Chief Fire Officer warned
OL,9,Fthat his Service does not have enough
OL,10,Fkit to protect firefighters due to a
OL,11,Flack of investment.
OL,13,FThe LGA report into the GFRS states
OL,14,Fthe lack of investment has resulted in
OL,15,Fa series of problems including:
