OL,3,CReport finds underinvestment in
OL,4,CGuernsey fire service puts public at
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FBefore the LGA review, the GFRS did
OL,8,Ftheir own assessment comparing itself
OL,9,Fto His Majesty's Inspectorate of
OL,10,FConstabulary and Fire & Rescue
OL,11,FServices areas of assessment and found
OL,12,Fof the 11 areas, two were inadequate
OL,13,Fand seven required improvement.
OL,15,FChief Fire Officer Les Britzman said
OL,16,Falthough all fire officers are doing
OL,17,Ftheir best, the GFRS needs investment
OL,18,Fto be the fire service they need to be.
