OL,7,FHe said: "It is my view that our teams
OL,8,Fare our greatest asset, and their
OL,9,Fcommitment to public safety is second
OL,10,Fto none. It is good to see this
OL,11,Freflected in the report. Equally, it
OL,12,Fis helpful to identify clear areas for
OL,13,Fus to focus on now, and with the
OL,14,Fsupport of the States of Guernsey, I
OL,15,Flook forward to implementing the
OL,16,Frecommendations and building on our
OL,17,Fstrong foundations to deliver the best
OL,18,Fpossible service to Guernsey and Herm."
