OL,7,FDeputy Marc Leadbeater, President of
OL,8,Fthe Committee for Home Affairs, said:
OL,9,F"This report is testament to the
OL,10,Fprofessionalism and commitment of the
OL,11,FGuernsey Fire & Rescue Service, and we
OL,12,Fshould all be grateful as islanders to
OL,13,Fknow they are ready to help us in an
OL,14,Femergency."
