OL,7,F"I am proud that the Service's
OL,8,Freputation and the trust it enjoys
OL,9,Facross the Bailiwick is highlighted by
OL,10,Fthe LGA, and the recommendations
OL,11,Fprovide a clear direction for
OL,12,Fstrengthening the Service further,
OL,13,Fensuring it remains resilient,
OL,14,Finnovative, and ready to meet the
OL,15,Fchallenges of the future."
